{"id":"destruction","term":"Destruction","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>In <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Job 26:6\">Job 26:6</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Job 27:14\">28</a>:22 (Heb. abaddon) is sheol, the realm of the dead.</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Job 26:6","Job 27:14"]}